---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="케이비(주) KB Inc. | 특장차 핵심 부품 — 에어서스펜션·액슬·유압실린더"
  active={null}
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[88vh] flex items-center border-b border-hairline-steel overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-graphite-surface opacity-40 -skew-x-12 translate-x-1/3 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center py-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-7" data-reveal>
        <p class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-arterial-red"></span>01 / <span data-ko-only>상용 특장차 부품</span><span data-en-only>HEAVY-VEHICLE COMPONENTS</span>
        </p>
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest text-[clamp(2.4rem,6vw,4.2rem)] leading-[1.08]">
          <span data-ko-only>전 세계가 신뢰하는<br /><span class="text-arterial-red">특장차 부품</span> 공급</span>
          <span data-en-only>Heavy-vehicle parts<br />the world <span class="text-arterial-red">relies on</span></span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-muted-zinc text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          <span data-ko-only>구주 및 미주 선진국의 검증된 공급선으로부터 에어서스펜션·액슬·유압실린더를 국내 특장차 시장에 안정적으로 공급합니다.</span>
          <span data-en-only>We supply air suspensions, axles, and hydraulic cylinders from proven European and American manufacturers to Korea's special-vehicle industry.</span>
        </p>
        <a href="/products" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-arterial-red text-bright-alloy font-mono text-sm px-8 py-4 active:translate-y-px hover:bg-arterial-red-dim transition-all">
          <span data-ko-only>제품 보기</span><span data-en-only>VIEW PRODUCTS</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative render-stage flex items-center justify-center md:min-h-[60vh]" data-reveal-x>
        <img src="/assets/img/mbs_hd_12t.gif" alt="VDL Weweler MBS-HD 12T 에어서스펜션" class="w-full max-w-[560px] h-auto object-contain drop-shadow-2xl animate-float" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BRAND BAR -->
  <section class="border-b border-hairline-steel bg-graphite-surface">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-8">
      <span class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-zinc whitespace-nowrap">PARTNER BRANDS</span>
      <div class="flex-grow grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
        <div class="logo-chip flex items-center justify-center h-16 px-4"><img src="/assets/img/VDL_Weweler_logo.gif" alt="VDL Weweler" class="max-h-7 w-auto" /></div>
        <div class="logo-chip flex items-center justify-center h-16 px-4"><img src="/assets/img/valx_logo.gif" alt="VALX" class="max-h-9 w-auto" /></div>
        <div class="logo-chip flex items-center justify-center h-16 px-4"><img src="/assets/img/penta_logo.gif" alt="HS Penta" class="max-h-9 w-auto" /></div>
        <div class="logo-chip flex items-center justify-center h-16 px-4"><img src="/assets/img/rolls_logo.gif" alt="ROLLS" class="max-h-12 w-auto" /></div>
        <div class="logo-chip flex items-center justify-center h-16 px-4 font-display font-bold text-xl text-charcoal-void tracking-tight col-span-2 sm:col-span-1">CIVACON</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRODUCT LINEUP -->
  <section id="products" class="border-b border-hairline-steel">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-section-v">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-16" data-reveal>
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red mb-3">01 / PRODUCTS</p>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem)]">
            <span data-ko-only>특장차 3대 핵심 부품</span><span data-en-only>Three core components</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-24 lg:gap-32">
        <!-- Row 01 suspension -->
        <article class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center group" data-reveal>
          <a href="/products#suspension" class="order-1 render-stage border border-hairline-steel bg-graphite-surface p-8 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden group-hover:border-arterial-red transition-colors">
            <img src="/assets/img/mbs_hd_12t.gif" alt="에어서스펜션" class="w-full max-h-[360px] object-contain group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
          </a>
          <div class="order-2 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 border-l border-hairline-steel pl-8 group-hover:border-arterial-red transition-colors">
            <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">01 / AIR SUSPENSION · VDL WEWELER</span>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-bright-alloy"><span data-ko-only>에어서스펜션</span><span data-en-only>Air Suspension</span></h3>
            <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed max-w-md">
              <span data-ko-only>90여 년 역사의 네덜란드 VDL Weweler. 유럽 시장 점유율 30% 이상, 완전 자동화된 최신 생산시설에서 생산되어 전 세계 모든 대륙에 공급됩니다.</span>
              <span data-en-only>Netherlands-based VDL Weweler, with over 90 years of history and a 30%+ European market share, produced in fully automated facilities and shipped to every continent.</span>
            </p>
            <a href="/products#suspension" class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-zinc hover:text-arterial-red inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
              <span data-ko-only>자세히</span><span data-en-only>DETAILS</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Row 02 axle -->
        <article class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center group" data-reveal>
          <a href="/products#axle" class="order-2 md:order-1 render-stage border border-hairline-steel bg-graphite-surface p-8 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden group-hover:border-arterial-red transition-colors">
            <img src="/assets/img/valx_disc500.gif" alt="VALX 액슬" class="w-full max-h-[240px] object-contain group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
          </a>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 border-l border-hairline-steel pl-8 group-hover:border-arterial-red transition-colors">
            <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">02 / AXLES · VALX</span>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-bright-alloy"><span data-ko-only>액슬</span><span data-en-only>Axles</span></h3>
            <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed max-w-md">
              <span data-ko-only>유럽 최고 기술로 설계·제작된 네덜란드 VALX 고품질 액슬. 드럼·디스크 브레이크 전 라인업에 Textar·WABCO·SKF·TIMKEN 등 세계적 부품을 채택했습니다.</span>
              <span data-en-only>High-quality VALX axles engineered in the Netherlands. Both drum and disc-brake lines use world-class components — Textar, WABCO, SKF, and TIMKEN.</span>
            </p>
            <a href="/products#axle" class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-zinc hover:text-arterial-red inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
              <span data-ko-only>자세히</span><span data-en-only>DETAILS</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Row 03 cylinder -->
        <article class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center group" data-reveal>
          <a href="/products#cylinder" class="order-1 render-stage border border-hairline-steel bg-graphite-surface p-8 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden group-hover:border-arterial-red transition-colors">
            <img src="/assets/img/penta_cylinders200.png" alt="HS Penta 유압실린더" class="w-full max-h-[360px] object-contain group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
          </a>
          <div class="order-2 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 border-l border-hairline-steel pl-8 group-hover:border-arterial-red transition-colors">
            <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">03 / HYDRAULIC CYLINDERS · HS PENTA</span>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-bright-alloy"><span data-ko-only>유압실린더</span><span data-en-only>Hydraulic Cylinders</span></h3>
            <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed max-w-md">
              <span data-ko-only>이탈리아 HS Penta (Inter Pump Group). 용접 없이 통 강관 내·외경을 직접 가공하여 대부분 200bar 압력에서 사용 가능한 고강성 다단 실린더를 생산합니다.</span>
              <span data-en-only>Italy's HS Penta (Inter Pump Group). Seamless tubes machined inside and out — no welds — for high-rigidity multi-stage cylinders rated for most applications at 200 bar.</span>
            </p>
            <a href="/products#cylinder" class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-zinc hover:text-arterial-red inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
              <span data-ko-only>자세히</span><span data-en-only>DETAILS</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY KB -->
  <section class="border-b border-hairline-steel">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-16 border-b border-hairline-steel" data-reveal>
      <p class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red mb-3">02 / CORE VALUES</p>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem)]">
        <span data-ko-only>케이비(주)를 선택하는 이유</span><span data-en-only>Why KB Inc.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter">
      <div class="border-b border-hairline-steel py-12 grid md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,20rem)_1fr] gap-6 md:gap-16 items-baseline group hover:bg-graphite-surface/40 transition-colors -mx-gutter px-gutter" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-bright-alloy flex items-center gap-4"><span class="font-mono text-sm text-arterial-red">A</span><span data-ko-only>최고의 품질</span><span data-en-only>Top Quality</span></h3>
        <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed">
          <span data-ko-only>구주 및 미주 선진국의 역사와 전통을 자랑하는 공급선으로부터 설계·개발·생산·품질관리에 이르기까지 최고의 기술과 최첨단 장비로 생산된 제품을 공급합니다. 모든 제품은 다년간 전 세계 시장에서 양산 적용되어 검증되었습니다.</span>
          <span data-en-only>Products engineered, built, and quality-controlled by long-established European and American manufacturers with the finest technology and equipment — each proven through years of volume production in markets worldwide.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-hairline-steel py-12 grid md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,20rem)_1fr] gap-6 md:gap-16 items-baseline group hover:bg-graphite-surface/40 transition-colors -mx-gutter px-gutter" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-bright-alloy flex items-center gap-4"><span class="font-mono text-sm text-arterial-red">B</span><span data-ko-only>경쟁력 있는 가격</span><span data-en-only>Competitive Price</span></h3>
        <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed">
          <span data-ko-only>다년간의 국제무역 경험을 바탕으로 운송비 절감과 운송절차 간소화 등 부수 비용을 최소화하여 가격 경쟁력을 확보했습니다. 북미에 이은 구주와의 자유무역협정으로 관세 또한 절감되는 추세입니다.</span>
          <span data-en-only>Years of international-trade experience minimize freight and handling costs, while free-trade agreements with North America and Europe continue to reduce tariffs — securing genuine price competitiveness.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-hairline-steel py-12 grid md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,20rem)_1fr] gap-6 md:gap-16 items-baseline group hover:bg-graphite-surface/40 transition-colors -mx-gutter px-gutter" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-bright-alloy flex items-center gap-4"><span class="font-mono text-sm text-arterial-red">C</span><span data-ko-only>책임지는 서비스</span><span data-en-only>Accountable Service</span></h3>
        <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed">
          <span data-ko-only>적용 검토 단계부터 발주·납품·사후관리에 이르는 전 과정을 책임집니다. 고객 입장에서 생각하는, 찾아가는 서비스로 고객만족을 위해 최선을 다합니다.</span>
          <span data-en-only>We take responsibility across the entire process — from application review to ordering, delivery, and after-sales support — with proactive, customer-first service.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-arterial-red">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest text-[clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.4rem)]">
        <span data-ko-only>부품 문의를 남겨주세요</span><span data-en-only>Send us your inquiry</span>
      </h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-bright-alloy text-bright-alloy font-mono text-sm px-8 py-4 hover:bg-bright-alloy hover:text-arterial-red active:translate-y-px transition-all">
        <span data-ko-only>문의하기</span><span data-en-only>CONTACT US</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">mail</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
